------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|leather items            |11.3                     |9.1                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|fur apparel              |3.0                      |5.7                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Footwear                 |26.4                     |14.6                     | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Fabric, all varieties    |9.5                      |5.9                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  Insofar as these commodities are being imported mainly 
through the funds of commercial structures and enterprises, the 
factor of effective demand exerts a decisive influence on 
changes in their structure. 


