<H3> <TI>   Decree, Statute on State Control of Land Use </TI></H3>
<H4>   Text of Decree </H4>
<F P=102> 944F0267A Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 14 Jan 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 944F0267A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:CSO 

<F P=106> [Decree of the Council of Ministers-Government of the </F>
Russian Federation of 23 December 1993, No. 1362, Moscow: "On 
Approval of the Statute on the Procedure for Exercising State 
Control Over the Utilization and Protection of Land in the 
Russian Federation"] 
  [Text] In execution of the Edicts of the President of the 
Russian Federation of 27 October 1993, No. 1767, "On Regulation 
of Land Relations and the Development of Agrarian Reform in 
Russia," and of 16 December 1993, No. 2162, "On Strengthening 
State Control Over the Utilization and Protection of Land While 
Conducting Land Reform," the Council of Ministers-Government of 
the Russian Federation decrees: 
  1. The appended Statute on the procedure for exercising 
state 
control over the utilization and protection of land in the 
Russian Federation shall be approved. 
  2. The Decree of the President of the Russian Federation of 
17 August 1992, No. 594, "On Approval of the Statute on the 
Procedure for Exercising State Control Over the Utilization and 
Protection of Land" (Collection of Documents of the President 
and Government of the Russian Federation, 1992, No. 8, p. 510) 
shall be declared invalid. 
  [Signed] Chairman of the Council of Ministers-Government of 
the Russian Federation V. Chernomyrdin 

