  Farms in the republic's border areas and the disaster zone 
produce 60.9 percent of the total volume of grain, 58.4 percent 
of potatoes, 24.3 percent of vegetables, 30.1 percent of fruit, 
8.7 percent of grapes, 64.0 percent of hay, 67.7 percent of 
straw, 42.7 percent of haylage, and 64.1 percent of silage. 
